This is how to is_multiply_prime of a:
  When a is at most 1, then:
    The answer is 0
  End when
  Remember that count is 0
  Remember that i is 2
  Do this a times:
    When product of i and i is more than a, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
    When remainder of a and i is 0, then:
      Increase count by 1
      When count is more than 1, then:
        The answer is 1
      End when
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is 0
